%E1%BB%A7-%C4%90%E1%BA%B1ng-V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-c%C3%A1c-c%E1%BB%91-ch%E1%BB%89/poem-paZKEMM-fSSJeT_i1hqUGw">Quá Nam Xương phủ Đằng Vương các cố chỉ - 過南昌府滕王閣故址</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-C%E1%BA%A3nh-Tu%C3%A2n/author-iFMRIrLpJEb-YMTvWL1HJQ">Lê Cảnh Tuân</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Khu%E1%BA%A5t-Nguy%C3%AAn/Thi%C3%AAn-v%E1%BA%A5n/poem-xfUL0RFU1M6WV9XOi__Sxg">Thiên vấn - 天問</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Khu%E1%BA%A5t-Nguy%C3%AAn/author-2RPFDWkSQLaYkT3rYIGIrQ">Khuất Nguyên</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Xu%C3%A2n-%C3%94n/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-t%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Bng-qu%C3%A2n-t%E1%BB%AB/poem-sXroCW2MVKXgcsaKmkN1ew">Trần tướng quân từ - 陳將軍祠</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Xu%C3%A2n-%C3%94n/author-MvAX8pIr0uu6mqdrhe1jhA">Nguyễn Xuân Ôn</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/T%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%C3%82m-d%E1%BA%A1/poem-grTLTd00-cFgfUKDV0weoA">Tương Âm dạ - 湘陰夜</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/author-ZRyB2U-4oqfhcjZ7xrf1_A">Nguyễn Du</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
